    "answer_id" : 61367144,
    "question_id" : 10463077,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>You can use <code>&lt;properties&gt;</code> tag to define a custom variable and <code>${variable}</code> pattern to use it </p>\n\n<pre><code>&lt;project xmlns=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0\" xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\" xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://maven.apache.org/POM/4.0.0 http://maven.apache.org/maven-v4_0_0.xsd\"&gt;\n\n    &lt;!-- define --&gt;\n    &lt;properties&gt;\n        &lt;property.name&gt;1.0&lt;/property.name&gt;\n    &lt;/properties&gt;\n\n    &lt;!-- using --&gt;\n    &lt;version&gt;${property.name}&lt;/version&gt;\n\n&lt;/project&gt;\n</code></pre>\n"
  } ],
